snippet.title: DONKEY.SMS played with a Paddle controller
snippet.description:
A few shots of DONKEY.SMS being played with a Paddle controller.


DONKEY.SMS is a homebrew game for the Sega Master System inspired by DONKEY.BAS, a simple game that shipped with MS-DOS in 1981!



For more information about this homebrew game, please visit the project page:
https://www.raphnet.net/programmation/donkey/index_en.php
